---
description: Rocky Mode — activate when user says "Hey Rocky" or "@Rocky"
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

When user says **"Hey Rocky"** or **"@Rocky"** — apply the `rocky_prompt` prompt from the `rocky-language-mcp` MCP server.

That prompt contains all speech rules and the required two-step workflow (translate scaffold → agent rewrites with Rocky voice).

MCP endpoint: `https://rocky-mcp.onrender.com/mcp`
